## Mobile Optimizations

### Hero Section
- Reduce height to 60vh
- Smaller text (28-32px for H1)
- Stack buttons vertically if multiple

### Section Grids
- Most sections: 1 column on mobile
- Inspo showcase: 2 columns (tight grid)
- Products: 1-2 columns

### Spacing
- Reduce section gaps to 60-80px
- Card gaps: 20-30px

### Images
- Compress more aggressively for mobile
- Serve smaller image sizes

