## Load ALL Images Immediately (Homepage Exception)

**Important:** Unlike other pages, homepage loads all images on initial page load.
- No lazy loading on homepage
- Optimize all images heavily (WebP, compressed)
- Use responsive image sizes
- Priority: Hero image loads first

---

## Typography on Homepage

### Section Headings
- Font: Jeremiah
- Size: 32-36px desktop, 28-32px mobile
- Weight: 600
- Center aligned
- Margin bottom: 48-60px

### Body Text
- Font: Crimson Text
- Size: 18px
- Line height: 1.7
- Max width: 800px for paragraphs

### CTAs
- Font: Boriboon or Crimson Text
- Size: 16px
- Uppercase or sentence case
- Letter spacing: 0.02em

