## Key Features to Maintain

1. **Dynamic content** - Pull latest blog posts, products from database/JSON
2. **Newsletter integration** - Keep form submission logic
3. **Links** - All sections link to respective full pages
4. **SEO** - Homepage meta tags, structured data
5. **Performance** - Fast load time despite multiple sections

